OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779822664
OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cand postpones surgeries
OL,6,FGuernsey's Princess Elizabeth Hospital
OL,7,Fhas declared a critical incident due
OL,8,Fto high demand.
OL,10,FSome elective surgeries have been
OL,11,Fpostponed for patient safety as the
OL,12,FStates of Guernsey says the
OL,13,FBailiwick's central healthcare
OL,14,Ffacility is over capacity.
OL,16,FThere is a warning of possible further
OL,17,Fdisruption over the coming days as
OL,18,Femergency surgery and cancer treatment
OL,19,Fare prioritised, with both scheduled
OL,20,Fto go ahead as planned.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779822664
OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cand postpones surgeries
OL,6,FThe situation is being monitored by a
OL,7,Fcritical incident team and officials
OL,8,Fsay any patients with disrupted
OL,9,Felective procedures will be contacted
OL,10,Fdirectly, with appointments rebooked
OL,11,Fas soon as possible.
OL,13,FTemporary beds have been brought in to
OL,14,Fhelp deal with the extra pressure on
OL,15,Fservices.
OL,17,FCommunity services and the Emergency
OL,18,FDepartment are also under strain due
OL,19,Fto increased workloads, with possible
OL,20,Flonger wait times for non-urgent cases.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779822664
OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cand postpones surgeries
OL,6,FIn a statement, Health and Social Care
OL,7,F(HSC) "recognises that it is always
OL,8,Fdisappointing when elective surgery
OL,9,Fmust be postponed and apologises for
OL,10,Fthe impact this has on individuals and
OL,11,Ftheir families".
OL,13,FIt explains "there is no single factor
OL,14,Fdriving the current level of
OL,15,Fadmissions" and that "the current
OL,16,Fhospital pressures are not linked to
OL,17,Fthe recent warmer weather".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
