CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779822664
OL,3,CHospital declares critical incident
OL,4,Cand postpones surgeries
OL,6,FHowever, HSC are urging everyone to
OL,7,Fdrink plenty of fluids, check on those
OL,8,Fwho may be in at-risk groups and use
OL,9,Fadequate sun protection to avoid
OL,10,Fputting further strain on services.
OL,12,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,13,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,14,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,15,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,16,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,17,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,18,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,19,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,20,FThursday...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/4
